---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const serviceTitle = 'AI SEO Starter Kit';
const metadata = {
  title: `${serviceTitle} - Capybara Studios`,
  description: `Jumpstart your organic growth with our ${serviceTitle}, an end-to-end AI-powered SEO solution.`,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">
          {serviceTitle}
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
          An end-to-end AI-powered SEO pipeline: keyword research, content generation, auto-publishing, and internal
          linking.
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose dark:prose-invert lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Challenge: Scaling Quality Content for SEO
          </h2>
          <p>
            Are you struggling to consistently produce high-quality, SEO-optimized content that ranks and drives organic
            traffic? Many businesses find it challenging to keep up with the demands of modern SEO, from in-depth
            keyword research to creating engaging articles and ensuring proper on-page optimization. Common pain points
            include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Difficulty identifying relevant keywords with good ranking potential.</li>
            <li>Time-consuming content creation processes that limit output.</li>
            <li>Inconsistent publishing schedules affecting SEO momentum.</li>
            <li>Struggles with effective internal linking to boost content authority.</li>
            <li>Keeping up with ever-changing search engine algorithms.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Capybara Studios Way: AI-Powered SEO Pipeline
          </h2>
          <p>
            Our AI SEO Starter Kit provides a fully automated, yet customizable, pipeline to supercharge your content
            strategy. We combine the power of AI with SEO best practices to deliver a sustainable solution for organic
            growth. Here's how it works:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3">
            <li>
              <strong>Strategic Keyword Research:</strong> We use AI tools to identify high-intent keywords and content opportunities
              relevant to your niche and target audience.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>AI-Assisted Content Generation:</strong> Leveraging advanced AI models, we help generate draft articles,
              blog posts, and other content optimized for your target keywords. This content is then refined and human-edited
              to ensure quality, accuracy, and brand voice.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated On-Page SEO:</strong> Our system ensures that essential on-page SEO elements (titles, meta
              descriptions, headers, image alt text) are optimized for each piece of content.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Auto-Scheduling & Publishing:</strong> We set up automated workflows to schedule and publish your content
              consistently across your chosen platforms (e.g., your blog, social media).
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Intelligent Internal Linking:</strong> Our system can automatically identify and create relevant internal
              links between your new and existing content, improving site navigation and distributing link equity.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Performance Monitoring Outline:</strong> We provide a framework for tracking key SEO metrics, allowing
              you to monitor performance and make data-driven adjustments.
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="mt-4">
            This kit is perfect for content-driven businesses looking to scale their SEO efforts efficiently and
            effectively, without needing a large in-house team.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center py-8 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            Ready to Boost Your Organic Traffic?
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
            Let our AI SEO Starter Kit lay the foundation for your search engine success.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3">Get Started with AI SEO</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

